Title: Street artist on the road
DateModified: '2019-03-07'
DatePublished: '2019-03-07'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/street-artist-on-the-road
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Ana Vizcaino Cabodevila
AuthorCountry: Spain
Text: "Through the point of view of street artist I would like to show how we can\
  \ understand the culture and way of life of the society of this country.\nTrying\
  \ to express and interact with the people by the eyes of the art. How another communication\
  \ is possible and what is the reaction of the native people about that. \nMusic,\
  \ songs, theater, juggling, clown, performance,... make us connect with those artist\
  \ who just want to exchange their skills with different proposes. \n\nLet they talk\
  \ with their own language, with their own art and how they make people think about..."
